   <div class="teaser_fmt"> 
    <h3>Anorexia Nervosa</h3> 
    <p>Anorexia nervosa is an eating disorder in which people have an intense fear of gaining weight and can become dangerously thin. Signs of anorexia include less than normal weight, negative body image, and obsession with food. </p> 
